  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 26033ac2059f0d64f984532c8b32d59c, type: 3}
  m_Name: Meet Cone
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  isDialogueSkippable: 1
  eventData:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: b0ab3d4ed062c8e4f9fca897dab8da3e, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: d18c853b77f69774693b1fc524348e8c, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: f7e08f12c324a9f489a0619efa32e49d, type: 2}
  dialogueLines:
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: No no no. What happened? Where'd all my customers go?
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Hey, you. Where did everyone go?
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: What? Really? A portal in the sky?
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: ...
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Thats terrible. All those profits, gone, just like that.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: I guess I setup the Trebapult for nothing.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: ...
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Hang on.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Your shapes are pretty important to you, right?
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: And you'd do anything to get them back?
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Great, then I can use you. I'll help you out.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: I've seen what you're describing before.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: I can take you there, but first, we'll have to make a stop.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Hop on the Trebapult, we'll say this first ride is a loan, with interest
      of course.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
